sequenceDiagram
    participant D as Driver
    participant S as System
    D->>D: Arrive at Bin Location
    D->>D: Empty Bin into Truck
    D->>S: Confirm Collection Completion (via App)
    S->>S: Reset Bin Fill Level to 0%
    S->>S: Record Timestamp & Location
    S->>D: Confirm Successful Update